snippet.title: ‘Aquaman’ Cast on Keeping Secrets, Aquababies & ‘The Snyder Cut’ | MTV News
snippet.description:
'Aquaman' stars Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, and Patrick Wilson talk with Josh Horowitz on the challenges of filming, various genres presented in the film, uncomfortable costumes, "Aquababies" and more. 

0:33 - Questions About Filming Conditions
2:09 - Rumors Confirmed
3:27 - Jason Apologizes to Josh
4:22 - The Superhero Genre Redefined
5:12 - Uncomfortable Costumes
7:13 - Amber’s Advice to Her Past Self 
7:54 - Watchmen vs. Aquaman
8:36 - Toughest Days on Set
9:40 - Aquaman Sequel
10:05 - The Snyder Cut
